\uc0\u10022  CLIENT ENERGY: (1-2 sentences)\
\uc0\u10022  EMOTIONAL ANCHORS: (what this session means to client)\
\uc0\u10022  SESSION PREP NOTES: (coaching notes for photographer)\
\uc0\u10022  STYLING NOTES: (wardrobe summary for photographer)`;\
